    "body": "## User visual authority\n\nAfter PR #256 merged to main `212597f49dd4d6cb2765f66921837d0af5ec8153`, the user visually rechecked the actual game and supplied a screenshot showing a standalone `⭐` toast directly below the permanent `⭐` stat anchor. The user also reported that Zoomer and Alpha still did not look meaningfully different in ordinary use. Therefore Stage 6 remains NOT COMPLETE.\n\n## Exact root causes\n\n1. The v2 helper `cleanOwnStatIcon()` stripped the anchor symbol but returned `cleaned || source`. For an icon-only toast such as `⭐`, `cleaned` becomes empty and the helper deliberately returned the original `⭐`, preserving the exact duplicate shown in the screenshot.\n2. The real delta emitter in `ui-core.js` creates `.statToast--delta` itself. v2 only post-processed those nodes and also skipped replacement when stripping the icon produced an empty string.\n3. PR #256 did create dictionary/control differences between Zoomer and Alpha, but too many were rare/state-dependent. Human visual acceptance requires differences on persistent/common surfaces, not merely a nonzero dictionary diff count.\n\n## Canon\n\nAlpha remains a delta over Zoomer, not a separate unrelated voice. It is shorter, more direct, lower-explanation, and fast/compact while preserving the same gameplay meaning and mechanics. The five accepted PR #245 frozen Alpha keys remain exact and are fail-closed in the v3 smoke:\n- `escape_button_label`\n- `teach_sent_dm`\n- `teach_sent_chat`\n- `invite_open_hint`\n- `invite_invalid`\n\n## Repair v3\n\n- Normalize stat toast text against the stat anchor symbol.\n  - icon-only `⭐` with delta `+1` becomes `+1`, not another `⭐`;\n  - `💰 +2` becomes `+2`;\n  - non-icon semantic text is preserved;\n  - non-delta icon-only redundant stat toast is suppressed.\n- Strengthen visible Zoomer/Alpha separation on persistent/common chrome:\n  - Zoomer: `Пиши по теме.` / `Заслать` / `Личка` / `Баттлы` / `Вброс` / `Ответка` / `Отвали` / `Свалить`.\n  - Alpha: `Сообщение` / `Отпр.` / `ЛС` / `Бои` / `Атк` / `Ответ` / `Стоп` / `Уйти`.\n- Shorten inherited/shared Alpha action/event copy while preserving the PR #245 frozen keys.\n- Add a profile watcher so direct profile changes cannot leave stale chrome until another unrelated render.\n- Keep all changes presentation-only. No economy values, battle rules, NPC behavior, handlers, state, persistence, prices, or outcomes change.\n\n## Smoke v3\n\n`Game.__DEV.smokeStage6FinalVisualToneRepairOnce()` now checks concrete human-visible contracts instead of generic dictionary-diff counts:\n- `alphaFrozenCopyPreserved`\n- at least 8 persistent Zoomer/Alpha chrome differences\n- Alpha persistent chrome shorter than Zoomer\n- Millennial escape currency clarity\n- no observed Boomer slang leakage\n- icon-only REP toast normalizes to `+1`\n- own-icon + numeric delta removes the duplicate icon\n- non-own semantic toast text remains intact\n- routing/toast/profile wrappers and profile watcher installed\n\n## Exact net diff\n\nBase: `212597f49dd4d6cb2765f66921837d0af5ec8153`\n\nExactly four paths:\n- `AsyncScene/Web/ui/ui-profile-visual-tone-repair.js`\n- `docs/ui/ui-profile-visual-tone-repair.js`\n- `AsyncScene/Web/index.html`\n- `docs/index.html`\n\nRepair mirrors are byte-identical at blob `fde0081a57ee27c657eb267f6b0007e18cd4d2f6`.\nIndex mirrors are byte-identical at blob `d1d9570b10c6af9d18b1358b7331bebb5848941d`.\nEach index changes exactly one cache-bust line from `20260722a` to `20260722b`.\n\nUser visual acceptance remains pending after merge. Stage 6 may not be declared COMPLETE from CI or smoke alone.",
